title: Storage not freeing up after "freeing up" space on Google Photos
content:
I've already backed up and freed up space using google photos but it doesn't seem to be clearing up the space on my phone.

I cannot find Chat support on my Google Pixel as well which is quite frustrating because I was able to access it just a few months ago.

This issue started occurring with the recent Android 11 update.
I have a Pixel 2 XL.

Please see screenshots for reference. All my whatsapp, and viber images have also been backed up and synced on Photos
